      "content": [
        {
          "type": "output_text",
          "text": "‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏à‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö!  \n‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠ **‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏î‡∏ä‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏™‡∏°‡∏ö‡∏π‡∏£‡∏ì‡πå** ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô Table Pattern Extraction & Workflow ‡∏•‡∏á CSV  \n+ ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ó‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏•‡∏•‡πå‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö clean, ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏° comment/debug, ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏≠‡∏î ML/Rule ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ\n\n---\n\n## **1. ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô Extract Transition Pattern (‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û)**\n\n```python\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom PIL import Image\n\ndef extract_transition_profile(image_path):\n    img = Image.open(image_path).convert('RGB')\n    arr = np.array(img)\n    height, width, _ = arr.shape\n    \n    # Result: (‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö per row)\n    records = []\n    for y in range(height):\n        row = arr[y]\n        diffs = np.any(row[1:] != row[:-1], axis=1)\n        x_points = [0] + (np.where(diffs)[0] + 1).tolist() + [width-1]\n        x_diffs = [x_points[i+1] - x_points[i] for i in range(len(x_points)-1)]\n\n        record = {\n            'Y': y,\n            'X Points': x_points,\n            'X Dif': x_diffs,\n            'X Count': len(x_points),\n            'X Dif Count': len(set(x_diffs)),\n            'X Dif Min': min(x_diffs) if x_diffs else None,\n            'X Dif Max': max(x_diffs) if x_diffs else None,\n            '# Comment': 'standard RGB pattern'\n        }\n        records.append(record)\n    # Return as DataFrame\n    return pd.DataFrame(records)\n\n# ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∂‡∏Å\ndf = extract_transition_profile('your_image.png')\ndf.to_csv('pattern_your_image.csv', index=False)\n```\n\n---\n\n## **2. ‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏•‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà: ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ & ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏´‡πå+‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏Ç‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á ‡πÜ**\n\n```python\nimport pandas as pd\n\n# ‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå csv ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà export ‡πÑ‡∏ß‡πâ\ndf = pd.read_csv('pattern_your_image.csv', converters={\"X Points\": eval, \"X Dif\": eval})\n\n# ‡∏î‡∏π transition profile ‡πÄ‡∏â‡∏û‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ß‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏™‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏à\nprint(df.head())\n\n# ‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏á step ‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏à‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° heuristic/‡∏ó‡∏î‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏á\n# ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á: ‡∏´‡∏≤ row ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô \"cluster text\" (`X Dif Max` ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≥/consistent), ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ \"cell boundary\" (`X Dif Max` ‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏ç‡πà)\nprint(df.loc[df['X Dif Max'] > 200])\n```\n\n---\n\n## **3. ‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏•‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà: ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå (batch ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢ heuristic)**\n\n```python\nimport glob\ndfs = []\nfor fname in glob.glob('pattern_*.csv'):\n    temp_df = pd.read_csv(fname, converters={\"X Points\": eval, \"X Dif\": eval})\n    temp_df['# File'] = fname\n    dfs.append(temp_df)\ndf_all = pd.concat(dfs, ignore_index=True)\n\n# ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á row/text pattern ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå\nprint(df_all[df_all['X Dif Max'] > 200][['# File','Y','X Points','X Dif Max']])\n```\n\n---\n\n## **4. ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ò‡∏µ Annotate/Compare ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ò‡∏µ (‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏ô‡∏ï‡πå‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ô csv ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢)**\n\n```python\n# ‡∏™‡∏°‡∏°‡∏∏‡∏ï‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏•‡∏±‡∏°‡∏ô‡πå/‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô logic ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏ì‡∏µ\ndf['# Comment'] = df.apply(\n    lambda row: 'maybe cell division' if row['X Dif Max'] > 500 else 'text cluster', axis=1)\ndf.to_csv('pattern_annotated.csv', index=False)\n```\n\n---\n\n## **5. Cell ‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏ó‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢: ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠ Mapping, ML, ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ Workflow ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠**\n\n```python\n# ‡∏≠‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå annotated ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏≥‡πÑ‡∏õ‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏£‡∏ô ML ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö OCR/‡∏≠‡∏∑‡πà‡∏ô ‡πÜ\ndf = pd.read_csv('pattern_annotated.csv', converters={\"X Points\": eval, \"X Dif\": eval})\n# ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ X/Y/transition mapping ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö bounding box ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°/ocr ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠ map to cell\n# (logic ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏° discussion ‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤)\n```\n\n---\n\n## **‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏µ workflow ‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ**\n- **clean, reproducible, modular:**  \n‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏•‡∏•‡πå‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å, logic ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏≠‡∏¥‡∏™‡∏£‡∏∞, csv debug ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏á‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢  \n- **comment ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå:**  \n‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà # ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏•‡∏±‡∏°‡∏ô‡πå desc ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏•‡∏∞ heuristic/‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡∏¥‡∏Ñ/‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏•‡∏±‡∏û‡∏ò‡πå  \n- **batch ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå pattern ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥**\n\n---\n\n### **‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏•‡∏ï‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ ‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡∏¥‡∏Ñ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà ML pursuer ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏ï‡πá‡∏°‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà  \n(‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö logic/report ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏´‡∏ô ‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢!)**"
