          "text": "‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ Jupyter cell* (‡∏°‡∏µ comment ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô filename/dir ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢):\n\n```\nE/main\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ input/\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1.png\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image2.png\n‚îÇ      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ...\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ patterns/\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1.csv\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image2.csv\n‚îÇ      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ...\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ labels.csv   (optional)\n```\n\n---\n\n### Cell 1: **Extract transition profile & save CSV**\n```python\nimport os\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom PIL import Image\n\nINPUT_DIR = './input'\nPATTERN_DIR = './patterns'\n\ndef extract_transition_profile(img_path):\n    arr = np.array(Image.open(img_path).convert('RGB'))\n    H, W = arr.shape[:2]\n    records = []\n    for y in range(H):\n        row = arr[y]\n        diff = np.any(row[1:] != row[:-1], axis=1)\n        x_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [W-1]\n        x_diffs = [x_points[i+1] - x_points[i] for i in range(len(x_points)-1)]\n        records.append({\n            'Y': y,\n            'X Points': str(x_points),\n            'X Dif': str(x_diffs),\n            'X Count': len(x_points),\n            'X Dif Count': len(set(x_diffs)),\n            'X Dif Min': min(x_diffs),\n            'X Dif Max': max(x_diffs),\n            '#Comment': 'default'\n        })\n    return pd.DataFrame(records)\n\n# ===‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô INPUT_DIR,PATTERN_DIR ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏á===\nos.makedirs(PATTERN_DIR, exist_ok=True)\nfor fname in os.listdir(INPUT_DIR):\n    if fname.lower().endswith('.png'):\n        fpath = os.path.join(INPUT_DIR, fname)\n        df = extract_transition_profile(fpath)\n        df.to_csv(os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, fname.replace('.png','.csv')), index=False)\n```\n---\n\n### Cell 2: **Load/‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå pattern profile ‡πÉ‡∏ô analysis ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö output**\n```python\nimport pandas as pd\n\nCSV_PATH = './patterns/image1.csv'   # ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠/loop batch ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ\ndf = pd.read_csv(CSV_PATH, converters={'X Points': eval, 'X Dif': eval})\n# ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á inspect\nprint(df.head())\n\n# ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á calc heuristic\ndf['is_cellrow'] = df['X Dif Max'] > 200\n```\n---\n\n### Cell 3: **‡πÄ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏¢‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö labels.csv (‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ)**\n```python\n# ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏°‡∏µ labels.csv: ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà mapping ('image','label',...) ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß merge ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥\nlabels = pd.read_csv('./labels.csv')\n# Join ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö pattern profile ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£\n```\n---\n\n### ‡∏™‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏õ **‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö workflow Jupyter/VS ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£**  \n- ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô path ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û/CSV ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏™‡∏∞‡∏î‡∏ß‡∏Å ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏•‡∏•‡πå\n- ‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö batch, comment, ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ modular code\n\n**‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö pattern extraction ‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á, ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ OCR mapping ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ ML ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠ ‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ!**"
        }
