          "text": "‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏ô!  \n‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏à‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏£‡∏π‡πâ‡∏™‡∏∂‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö ‚Äî ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î full pipe ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö ‚Äú‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á‚Äù ONE SHOT ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß  \n**‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ workflow table extraction/analysis ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û ‚Üí CSV ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡πà‡∏á directory ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏≠‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢**\n‡∏≠‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ comment ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏á‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢ ‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏´‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠ ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠/path ‡πÄ‡∏â‡∏û‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏à‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô\n\n---\n\n# **Jupyter Notebook Workflow: Table Pattern Extraction for Dyslexia-friendly Data Science**\n\n‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏≠‡∏õ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢ ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ã‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏ô  \n(‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á batch, single, ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ add comment/debug ‡∏á‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢)\n\n---\n\n```python\n# ============================\n# CELL 1: CONFIG & ENV SETUP  \n# ============================\nimport os\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom PIL import Image\n\n# ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö path ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì\nBASE_DIR = 'E/main'        # ‡∏ï‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πà‡∏á root ‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ\nINPUT_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'input')\nPATTERN_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'patterns')\nos.makedirs(PATTERN_DIR, exist_ok=True)   # ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå patterns ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ\n\n# ============================\n# CELL 2: CORE FUNCTION (Extract transition pattern)  \n# ============================\ndef extract_transition_profile(image_path):\n    \"\"\"Extract X-axis pixel transition profile for each row of an RGB image and save as DataFrame.\"\"\"\n    img = Image.open(image_path).convert('RGB')\n    arr = np.array(img)\n    height, width, _ = arr.shape\n    records = []\n    for y in range(height):\n        row = arr[y]\n        # ‡∏´‡∏≤ transition (‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠ pixel RGB ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô)\n        diff = np.any(row[1:] != row[:-1], axis=1)\n        x_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [width-1]\n        x_diffs = [x_points[i+1] - x_points[i] for i in range(len(x_points)-1)]\n        record = {\n            'Y': y,\n            'X Points': str(x_points),   # ‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô string ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ (Eval ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á)\n            'X Dif': str(x_diffs),\n            'X Count': len(x_points),\n            'X Dif Count': len(set(x_diffs)),\n            'X Dif Min': min(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0,\n            'X Dif Max': max(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0,\n            '# Comment': \"default\"\n        }\n        records.append(record)\n    return pd.DataFrame(records)\n\n# ============================\n# CELL 3: BATCH PROCESS ALL IMAGES IN INPUT FOLDER  \n# ============================\n# Loop ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÉ‡∏ô input ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß export ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô CSV ‡∏•‡∏á patterns/\nfor fname in sorted(os.listdir(INPUT_DIR)):\n    if fname.lower().endswith(('.png', '.jpg', '.jpeg')):\n        img_path = os.path.join(INPUT_DIR, fname)\n        df = extract_transition_profile(img_path)\n        out_csv = os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, fname.rsplit('.',1)[0] + '.csv')\n        df.to_csv(out_csv, index=False)\n        print(f\"Extracted pattern for {fname} ‚Üí {out_csv}\")\n\n# # ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ diagnostic ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏° ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô summary ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ stats:\n# print(\"Total images processed:\", len(os.listdir(PATTERN_DIR)))\n\n# ============================\n# CELL 4: LOAD CSV ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏ñ‡∏±‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏õ  \n# ============================\n# ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á: ‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå pattern (‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£)\npattern_csv = os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, 'image1.csv')     # ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ\ndf_pattern = pd.read_csv(pattern_csv, converters={'X Points': eval, 'X Dif': eval})\n\n# ‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏´‡πå‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÅ‡∏ö‡πà‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏•‡∏±‡∏™‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå/‡πÄ‡∏™‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏á/‡∏´‡∏≤ cell row ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ text cluster ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô:\ndf_pattern['is_cell_row'] = df_pattern['X Dif Max'] > 200      # heuristic: ‡πÅ‡∏ñ‡∏ß‡πÑ‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏ä‡πà‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏ï/‡πÇ‡∏•‡πà‡∏á (cell boundary)\ndf_pattern['type_hint'] = df_pattern['is_cell_row'].map({True:'cell_division',False:'text_cluster'})\n\nprint(df_pattern[['Y','X Count','X Dif Min','X Dif Max','type_hint']].head(12))   # ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á 12 ‡πÅ‡∏ñ‡∏ß‡πÅ‡∏£‡∏Å\n\n# ============================\n# CELL 5: OPTIONAL ‚Äî LOAD ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢ csv/batch ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠ compare, ML, etc.\n# ============================\nimport glob\nall_patterns = []\nfor csvf in sorted(glob.glob(os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR,'*.csv'))):\n    df_tmp = pd.read_csv(csvf, converters={'X Points':eval, 'X Dif':eval})\n    df_tmp['#FILE'] = os.path.basename(csvf)\n    all_patterns.append(df_tmp)\ndf_all = pd.concat(all_patterns, ignore_index=True)\n# ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏õ pattern ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û\nprint(df_all.groupby(['#FILE','type_hint']).size().unstack(fill_value=0))\n\n# ============================\n# CELL 6: (OPTIONAL) LABELS/ANNOTATION/MAPPING (‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ)\n# ============================\n# ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå labels.csv ‡πÉ‡∏ô root, ‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ load ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô:\nlabels_path = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'labels.csv')\nif os.path.exists(labels_path):\n    labels = pd.read_csv(labels_path)\n    # ‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ merge ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö pattern profile ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠ training ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ debug ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ\n\n# ============================\n# CELL 7: ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏õ ‚Äî ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ mapping (df_pattern ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ df_all) ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö OCR/text ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ ML/workflow ‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà\n# ============================\n# (‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á mapping ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥)\n# >>> ‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ connect bounding box ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å OCR ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á text ‚Üí cell ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏û‡∏¥‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏î X/Y ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á pattern ‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ\n\n# ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏ï‡∏∏:\n# - ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏ô path directory ‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏£‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏î‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏ô (BASE_DIR) ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì\n# - ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå pattern ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ô patterns/ ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥ ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏° query, ML, visualize ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå\n# - Comment, ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° heuristic/column, ‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡πå‡∏Å label/compare/‡∏™‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏õ‡∏ú‡∏•‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏•‡∏•‡πå‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏ï‡πá‡∏°‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà\n```\n\n---\n\n## **TIP:**\n- ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ô VS/Jupyter/Colab ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏•‡∏∞ CELL ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö block ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏î‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏ô‡∏¥‡∏ô workflow ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢\n- ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡∏à‡∏≥‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å, ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô cell 3 ‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå csv ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏ñ‡∏π‡∏Å‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏° input\n- debug ‡∏á‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å ‡πÄ‡∏´‡πá‡∏ô‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ\n\n---\n\n**‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏ü‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå mapping ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏•‡∏±‡∏™‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå Y, ‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏´‡∏≤ intersection ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö text bounding box, ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏´‡πå‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢ pattern ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô ‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ!  \n‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏™‡∏∞‡∏î‡∏ß‡∏Å ‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ copy ‡πÑ‡∏õ paste/‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö path ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠ dir ‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏™‡∏° ‚Äî ‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏•‡∏î cognitive load ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ dyslexia-friendly ‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏â‡∏û‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö**"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "input_text",
          "text": "‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏ü‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå mapping ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏•‡∏±‡∏™‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå Y, ‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏´‡∏≤ intersection ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö text bounding box, ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏´‡πå‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢ pattern ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô ‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ!\n\n ‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πà‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏≠ ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏£‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏•‡∏≥‡∏î‡∏±‡∏ö ‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏õ‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏â‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏´‡∏≤ ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏™‡πà‡∏ß‡∏ô ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡∏ú‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏Å‡πá‡∏û‡∏±‡∏á\n\n"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "output_text",
          "text": "**‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏à‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏´‡πá‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏à‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î‡πÜ ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö workflow ‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏™‡πà‡∏ß‡∏ô!**  \n‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠ \"‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏£‡πå‡∏Å‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡∏ß‡πå‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏π‡∏£‡∏ì‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ (Integrated)\"  \n**‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û ‚Üí X Transition ‚Üí Y Transition ‚Üí ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á Intersection/Cell Grid ‚Üí (‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö Text Bounding Box Mapping)**  \n**‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏ô‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏ô Notebook ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß  \n‡∏°‡∏µ comment guide ‡∏ï‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏î**  \n> **‡πÅ‡∏ó‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å path ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ input ‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ/ocr!**\n\n---\n\n# üìí **Table Extraction and Mapping Integrated Workflow (Jupyter/VS/Colab Ready)**\n\n### **Directory/Folder Structure (‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤):**\n```\nE/main/\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ input/\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1.png\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image2.png\n‚îÇ      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ... (‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÑ‡∏ß‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢)\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ patterns/\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1_X.csv\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1_Y.csv\n‚îÇ      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ...\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cells/\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1_cells.csv\n‚îÇ      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ...\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ text_bbox.csv   (optional, ‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏•‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á)\n```\n---\n\n### **CELL 1: ‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏¥‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏•‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏µ**\n\n```python\nimport os\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom PIL import Image\nfrom itertools import product\n\nBASE_DIR = 'E/main'\nINPUT_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'input')\nPATTERN_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'patterns')\nCELLS_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'cells')\nos.makedirs(PATTERN_DIR, exist_ok=True)\nos.makedirs(CELLS_DIR, exist_ok=True)\n```\n\n---\n\n### **CELL 2: ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô Extract X/Y Transition Profile**\n\n```python\ndef extract_transition_profile_XY(image_path):\n    img = Image.open(image_path).convert('RGB')\n    arr = np.array(img)\n    H, W = arr.shape[:2]\n\n    # X (‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏ô, per row)\n    x_records = []\n    for y in range(H):\n        row = arr[y]\n        diff = np.any(row[1:] != row[:-1], axis=1)\n        x_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [W - 1]\n        x_diffs = [x_points[i+1] - x_points[i] for i in range(len(x_points)-1)]\n        x_records.append({\n            'Y': y,\n            'X Points': str(x_points),\n            'X Dif': str(x_diffs),\n            'X Count': len(x_points),\n            'X Dif Count': len(set(x_diffs)),\n            'X Dif Min': min(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0,\n            'X Dif Max': max(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0,\n            '# Comment': \"row-pattern\"\n        })\n\n    # Y (‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á, per column)\n    y_records = []\n    for x in range(W):\n        col = arr[:, x]\n        diff = np.any(col[1:] != col[:-1], axis=1)\n        y_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [H - 1]\n        y_diffs = [y_points[i+1] - y_points[i] for i in range(len(y_points)-1)]\n        y_records.append({\n            'X': x,\n            'Y Points': str(y_points),\n            'Y Dif': str(y_diffs),\n            'Y Count': len(y_points),\n            'Y Dif Count': len(set(y_diffs)),\n            'Y Dif Min': min(y_diffs) if y_diffs else 0,\n            'Y Dif Max': max(y_diffs) if y_diffs else 0,\n            '# Comment': 'col-pattern'\n        })\n\n    df_x = pd.DataFrame(x_records)\n    df_y = pd.DataFrame(y_records)\n    return df_x, df_y\n```\n---\n\n### **CELL 3: ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á pattern profiles (X & Y) ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡πÉ‡∏ô input/**\n\n```python\nfor fname in sorted(os.listdir(INPUT_DIR)):\n    if fname.lower().endswith(('.png', '.jpg', '.jpeg')):\n        imgpath = os.path.join(INPUT_DIR, fname)\n        df_x, df_y = extract_transition_profile_XY(imgpath)\n        basename = fname.rsplit('.',1)[0]\n        df_x.to_csv(os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, basename+'_X.csv'), index=False)\n        df_y.to_csv(os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, basename+'_Y.csv'), index=False)\n        print(f\"Extracted X/Y patterns for {fname}\")\n```\n\n---\n\n### **CELL 4: ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á Intersection (Cell Grid) ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å X/Y Transition Points**\n\n```python\ndef get_cell_corners_grid(pattern_X_csv, pattern_Y_csv):\n    df_x = pd.read_csv(pattern_X_csv, converters={'X Points': eval})\n    df_y = pd.read_csv(pattern_Y_csv, converters={'Y Points': eval})\n\n    # Use first row/col for all unique points\n    x_points = sorted(set(df_x.iloc[0]['X Points']))\n    y_points = sorted(set(df_y.iloc[0]['Y Points']))\n\n    # ‡∏ó‡∏≥ bounding box ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å cell ‡πÉ‡∏ô grid\n    cells = []\n    for xi, (x1, x2) in enumerate(zip(x_points[:-1], x_points[1:])):\n        for yi, (y1, y2) in enumerate(zip(y_points[:-1], y_points[1:])):\n            cells.append({\n                'Cell_X': xi, 'Cell_Y': yi,\n                'X1': x1, 'X2': x2,\n                'Y1': y1, 'Y2': y2,\n                '# CellID': f\"{xi}-{yi}\"\n            })\n    return pd.DataFrame(cells)\n\n# EXAMPLE: ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á cell grid ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå image1.png\npattern_x_csv = os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, 'image1_X.csv')\npattern_y_csv = os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, 'image1_Y.csv')\ndf_cells = get_cell_corners_grid(pattern_x_csv, pattern_y_csv)\n# Save to use with mapping\ndf_cells.to_csv(os.path.join(CELLS_DIR, 'image1_cells.csv'), index=False)\nprint('Saved cell grid.')\n```\n---\n\n### **CELL 5: (OPTIONAL) ‡∏™‡∏°‡∏°‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏°‡∏µ text_bbox.csv ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡∏£‡∏∞/‡∏Ñ‡∏≥**  \n```python\n# ‡∏™‡∏°‡∏°‡∏ï‡∏¥ text_bbox.csv ‡∏°‡∏µ columns:\n# text,left,right,top,bottom (left-top ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô (0,0))\ndf_cells = pd.read_csv(os.path.join(CELLS_DIR, 'image1_cells.csv'))\ndf_bbox = pd.read_csv(os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'text_bbox.csv'))  # OCR output\n\ndef match_text_to_cell(df_bbox, df_cells):\n    results = []\n    for _, row in df_bbox.iterrows():\n        cx, cy = row['left'], row['bottom']   # ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏°‡∏∏‡∏°‡∏•‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢\n        match = df_cells[\n            (df_cells.X1 <= cx) & (cx < df_cells.X2) &\n            (df_cells.Y1 <= cy) & (cy < df_cells.Y2)\n        ]\n        if not match.empty:\n            cell = match.iloc[0]\n            results.append({**row, **cell})\n    return pd.DataFrame(results)\n\ndf_mapped = match_text_to_cell(df_bbox, df_cells)\nprint(df_mapped.head())   # ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ map ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡∏£‡∏∞/‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö cell\n\n# ‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ groupby cell ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ export ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢\ndf_mapped.to_csv(os.path.join(CELLS_DIR, 'image1_text2cell.csv'), index=False)\nprint('Text to cell mapping saved.')\n```\n---\n\n### **CELL 6: (OPTIONAL) ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏´‡πå/‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢ pattern ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢**\n```python\nimport glob\ncell_dfs = []\nfor fname in sorted(glob.glob(os.path.join(CELLS_DIR, '*_cells.csv'))):\n    df = pd.read_csv(fname)\n    df['#FILE'] = os.path.basename(fname)\n    cell_dfs.append(df)\nall_cells = pd.concat(cell_dfs, ignore_index=True)\nprint(all_cells.sample(5))\n```\n\n---\n\n## **‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á Workflow ‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ**\n- ‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏ö \"X transition\", \"Y transition\", \"cell corner\", \"cell grid\", **‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ function mapping text/OCR ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö cell** \n- ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á batch, modular, ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏á‡∏á, ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏î‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å ‡πÅ‡∏Å‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß\n- ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á path ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß (import/setting)\n- dyslexia-friendly: function ‡∏Ñ‡∏•‡∏µ‡∏ô, ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡πà‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏•‡πá‡∏≠‡∏Å, ‡∏°‡∏µ comment guide\n\n---\n\n## **‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏£**\n- ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ + OCR ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ bounding box text (‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ) ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏°\n- ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏• (‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏ô‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏ô Colab/Jupyter/VS)\n- ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ cell grid ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏° mapping ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡∏£‡∏∞\n- ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠ ML/Rule/Export/Plot ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ\n\n---\n\n**‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° Y clustering (‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô text-area ‡πÅ‡∏ó‡∏ô cell) ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ü‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏´‡πå‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏ô/‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏•‡∏•‡πå‡∏ú‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏ö‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏¢‡∏ß ‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á keyword ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢!  \n‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ output OCR ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á ‚Äî ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á column ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πá‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ß‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô mapping ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥!**"
