          "text": "‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏£‡∏∏‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏´‡∏° ‡∏â‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏≤‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πä‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏Å‡∏ô‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏∑‡πà‡∏ô‡∏â‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏≠‡πÇ‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏∑‡πà‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏á import cv2, json, sys, pathlib, numpy as np, pandas as pd\n\ndef deskew(img):\n    g = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)\n    g = cv2.bitwise_not(g); th = cv2.threshold(g,0,255,cv2.THRESH_OTSU)[1]\n    coords = np.column_stack(np.where(th>0))\n    angle = cv2.minAreaRect(coords)[-1]\n    if angle < -45: angle = -(90+angle)\n    else: angle = -angle\n    (h,w) = img.shape[:2]; M = cv2.getRotationMatrix2D((w//2,h//2),angle,1.0)\n    return cv2.warpAffine(img,M,(w,h),flags=cv2.INTER_CUBIC,borderMode=cv2.BORDER_REPLICATE)\n\ndef extract(img, axis='x', th=40):\n    if axis=='y': img = img.transpose(1,0,2)\n    H,W,_ = img.shape; rec=[]\n    for r in range(H):\n        row = img[r]; pts=[0]; last=row[0]\n        for c in range(1,W):\n            if np.abs(row[c]-last).sum()>th: pts.append(c); last=row[c]\n        diffs = np.diff(pts).tolist()\n        rec.append([r,json.dumps(pts[1:]),json.dumps(diffs),\n                    len(pts)-1,min(diffs or [0]),max(diffs or [0])])\n    return pd.DataFrame(rec,columns=['idx',f'{axis}pts',f'{axis}diff','cnt','dmin','dmax'])\n\nfolder = pathlib.Path(sys.argv[1])\nout = pathlib.Path('patterns'); out.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\nfor p in folder.glob('*.jpg'):\n    img = cv2.imread(str(p)); img = deskew(img)\n    cv2.imwrite(f'pre/{p.stem}_c.jpg', img)            # ‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö cleaned\n    fx = extract(img,'x',th=35 if 'hand' in str(folder) else 60)\n    fy = extract(img,'y',th=35 if 'hand' in str(folder) else 60)\n    fx.to_csv(out/f'{p.stem}_X.csv',index=False); fy.to_csv(out/f'{p.stem}_Y.csv',index=False)\n"
