          "text": "\n‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πä‡∏î‡∏ú‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î \n\n**‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏à‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏´‡πá‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏à‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î‡πÜ ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö workflow ‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏™‡πà‡∏ß‡∏ô!**  \n‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠ \"‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏£‡πå‡∏Å‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡∏ß‡πå‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏π‡∏£‡∏ì‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ (Integrated)\"  \n**‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û ‚Üí X Transition ‚Üí Y Transition ‚Üí ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á Intersection/Cell Grid ‚Üí (‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö Text Bounding Box Mapping)**  \n**‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏ô‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏ô Notebook ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß  \n‡∏°‡∏µ comment guide ‡∏ï‡∏•‡∏≠‡∏î**  \n> **‡πÅ‡∏ó‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å path ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ input ‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ/ocr!**\n\n---\n\n# üìí **Table Extraction and Mapping Integrated Workflow (Jupyter/VS/Colab Ready)**\n\n### **Directory/Folder Structure (‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤):**\n```\nE/main/\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ input/\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1.png\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image2.png\n‚îÇ      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ... (‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÑ‡∏ß‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢)\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ patterns/\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1_X.csv\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1_Y.csv\n‚îÇ      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ...\n‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cells/\n‚îÇ      ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ image1_cells.csv\n‚îÇ      ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ...\n‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ text_bbox.csv   (optional, ‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏•‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á)\n```\n---\n\n### **CELL 1: ‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏¥‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏•‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏µ**\n\n```python\nimport os\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom PIL import Image\nfrom itertools import product\n\nBASE_DIR = 'E/main'\nINPUT_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'input')\nPATTERN_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'patterns')\nCELLS_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'cells')\nos.makedirs(PATTERN_DIR, exist_ok=True)\nos.makedirs(CELLS_DIR, exist_ok=True)\n```\n\n---\n\n### **CELL 2: ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô Extract X/Y Transition Profile**\n\n```python\ndef extract_transition_profile_XY(image_path):\n    img = Image.open(image_path).convert('RGB')\n    arr = np.array(img)\n    H, W = arr.shape[:2]\n\n    # X (‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏ô, per row)\n    x_records = []\n    for y in range(H):\n        row = arr[y]\n        diff = np.any(row[1:] != row[:-1], axis=1)\n        x_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [W - 1]\n        x_diffs = [x_points[i+1] - x_points[i] for i in range(len(x_points)-1)]\n        x_records.append({\n            'Y': y,\n            'X Points': str(x_points),\n            'X Dif': str(x_diffs),\n            'X Count': len(x_points),\n            'X Dif Count': len(set(x_diffs)),\n            'X Dif Min': min(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0,\n            'X Dif Max': max(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0,\n            '# Comment': \"row-pattern\"\n        })\n\n    # Y (‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á, per column)\n    y_records = []\n    for x in range(W):\n        col = arr[:, x]\n        diff = np.any(col[1:] != col[:-1], axis=1)\n        y_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [H - 1]\n        y_diffs = [y_points[i+1] - y_points[i] for i in range(len(y_points)-1)]\n        y_records.append({\n            'X': x,\n            'Y Points': str(y_points),\n            'Y Dif': str(y_diffs),\n            'Y Count': len(y_points),\n            'Y Dif Count': len(set(y_diffs)),\n            'Y Dif Min': min(y_diffs) if y_diffs else 0,\n            'Y Dif Max': max(y_diffs) if y_diffs else 0,\n            '# Comment': 'col-pattern'\n        })\n\n    df_x = pd.DataFrame(x_records)\n    df_y = pd.DataFrame(y_records)\n    return df_x, df_y\n```\n---\n\n### **CELL 3: ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á pattern profiles (X & Y) ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡πÉ‡∏ô input/**\n\n```python\nfor fname in sorted(os.listdir(INPUT_DIR)):\n    if fname.lower().endswith(('.png', '.jpg', '.jpeg')):\n        imgpath = os.path.join(INPUT_DIR, fname)\n        df_x, df_y = extract_transition_profile_XY(imgpath)\n        basename = fname.rsplit('.',1)[0]\n        df_x.to_csv(os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, basename+'_X.csv'), index=False)\n        df_y.to_csv(os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, basename+'_Y.csv'), index=False)\n        print(f\"Extracted X/Y patterns for {fname}\")\n```\n\n---\n\n### **CELL 4: ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á Intersection (Cell Grid) ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å X/Y Transition Points**\n\n```python\ndef get_cell_corners_grid(pattern_X_csv, pattern_Y_csv):\n    df_x = pd.read_csv(pattern_X_csv, converters={'X Points': eval})\n    df_y = pd.read_csv(pattern_Y_csv, converters={'Y Points': eval})\n\n    # Use first row/col for all unique points\n    x_points = sorted(set(df_x.iloc[0]['X Points']))\n    y_points = sorted(set(df_y.iloc[0]['Y Points']))\n\n    # ‡∏ó‡∏≥ bounding box ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å cell ‡πÉ‡∏ô grid\n    cells = []\n    for xi, (x1, x2) in enumerate(zip(x_points[:-1], x_points[1:])):\n        for yi, (y1, y2) in enumerate(zip(y_points[:-1], y_points[1:])):\n            cells.append({\n                'Cell_X': xi, 'Cell_Y': yi,\n                'X1': x1, 'X2': x2,\n                'Y1': y1, 'Y2': y2,\n                '# CellID': f\"{xi}-{yi}\"\n            })\n    return pd.DataFrame(cells)\n\n# EXAMPLE: ‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á cell grid ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå image1.png\npattern_x_csv = os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, 'image1_X.csv')\npattern_y_csv = os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, 'image1_Y.csv')\ndf_cells = get_cell_corners_grid(pattern_x_csv, pattern_y_csv)\n# Save to use with mapping\ndf_cells.to_csv(os.path.join(CELLS_DIR, 'image1_cells.csv'), index=False)\nprint('Saved cell grid.')\n```\n---\n\n### **CELL 5: (OPTIONAL) ‡∏™‡∏°‡∏°‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏°‡∏µ text_bbox.csv ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡∏£‡∏∞/‡∏Ñ‡∏≥**  \n```python\n# ‡∏™‡∏°‡∏°‡∏ï‡∏¥ text_bbox.csv ‡∏°‡∏µ columns:\n# text,left,right,top,bottom (left-top ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô (0,0))\ndf_cells = pd.read_csv(os.path.join(CELLS_DIR, 'image1_cells.csv'))\ndf_bbox = pd.read_csv(os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'text_bbox.csv'))  # OCR output\n\ndef match_text_to_cell(df_bbox, df_cells):\n    results = []\n    for _, row in df_bbox.iterrows():\n        cx, cy = row['left'], row['bottom']   # ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏°‡∏∏‡∏°‡∏•‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢\n        match = df_cells[\n            (df_cells.X1 <= cx) & (cx < df_cells.X2) &\n            (df_cells.Y1 <= cy) & (cy < df_cells.Y2)\n        ]\n        if not match.empty:\n            cell = match.iloc[0]\n            results.append({**row, **cell})\n    return pd.DataFrame(results)\n\ndf_mapped = match_text_to_cell(df_bbox, df_cells)\nprint(df_mapped.head())   # ‡πÅ‡∏™‡∏î‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ map ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡∏£‡∏∞/‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö cell\n\n# ‡∏™‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ñ groupby cell ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ export ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢\ndf_mapped.to_csv(os.path.join(CELLS_DIR, 'image1_text2cell.csv'), index=False)\nprint('Text to cell mapping saved.')\n```\n---\n\n### **CELL 6: (OPTIONAL) ‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏´‡πå/‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡πÄ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢ pattern ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢**\n```python\nimport glob\ncell_dfs = []\nfor fname in sorted(glob.glob(os.path.join(CELLS_DIR, '*_cells.csv'))):\n    df = pd.read_csv(fname)\n    df['#FILE'] = os.path.basename(fname)\n    cell_dfs.append(df)\nall_cells = pd.concat(cell_dfs, ignore_index=True)\nprint(all_cells.sample(5))\n```\n\n---\n\n## **‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á Workflow ‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ**\n- ‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏ö \"X transition\", \"Y transition\", \"cell corner\", \"cell grid\", **‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ function mapping text/OCR ‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö cell** \n- ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á batch, modular, ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏á‡∏á, ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏µ‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏î‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å ‡πÅ‡∏Å‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß\n- ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á path ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß (import/setting)\n- dyslexia-friendly: function ‡∏Ñ‡∏•‡∏µ‡∏ô, ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡πà‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏•‡πá‡∏≠‡∏Å, ‡∏°‡∏µ comment guide\n\n---\n\n## **‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏£**\n- ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ + OCR ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ bounding box text (‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ) ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏°\n- ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏• (‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡πÄ‡∏ô‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏ô Colab/Jupyter/VS)\n- ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ cell grid ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏° mapping ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏Å‡∏Ç‡∏£‡∏∞\n- ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠ ML/Rule/Export/Plot ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ\n\n---\n\n**‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° Y clustering (‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô text-area ‡πÅ‡∏ó‡∏ô cell) ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏ü‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏ß‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏∞‡∏´‡πå‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏∏‡πà‡∏°‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏ô/‡πÄ‡∏ã‡∏•‡∏•‡πå‡∏ú‡∏¥‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏ö‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏¢‡∏ß ‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á keyword ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢!  \n‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ output OCR ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á ‚Äî ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á column ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πá‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ß‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô mapping ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥!**\n\n‡∏â‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏à‡πâ‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÑ‡∏ß‡πâ ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ ‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà image_path\n\n‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏Å‡∏π‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô Dyslexia ‡πÅ‡∏ó‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏°‡∏µ‡πÅ‡∏°‡πâ‡∏á‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏≠‡∏ò‡∏¥‡∏ö‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏´‡∏ô ‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î \n\n‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏°‡∏∂‡∏á‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏î‡∏µ ‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Å‡∏π‡∏£‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏™‡∏ï‡πå‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠ \"‡∏≠‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ß ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏≠ ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢ ‡πÄ‡∏´‡πá‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏à‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô Dyslexia ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏à‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏≠‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πä‡∏î‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢\" ‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏Ñ‡∏ô‡∏•‡∏∞‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢"
