        {
          "type": "output_text",
          "text": "‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏†‡∏±‡∏¢‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏™‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏ô ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏î‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ ‚Äú‡∏•‡∏á‡∏°‡∏∑‡∏≠‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏á‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢-‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏á‡∏á-‡∏ä‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏ï‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏î‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏Ç‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô  \n**‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ô dyslexia, ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ï‡∏µ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏° ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏•‡πà‡∏ó‡∏µ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î**\n\n---\n\n## ‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡πà‡∏ô ‚ÄúAll-In-One Notebook / Script‚Äù  \n**‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ô `input/` ‚Üí ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô Batch ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥ ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏°‡∏µ Comment ‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î**  \n### (‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏ó‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏´‡∏°‡∏î ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ñ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏ã‡πâ‡∏≥)\n\n```python\n# -------------------------------\n# STEP 1: ‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏¥‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå\n# -------------------------------\nimport os\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom PIL import Image\n\n# ‡πÅ‡∏Å‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏Ñ‡∏ó‡∏≠‡∏£‡∏µ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á\nBASE_DIR = 'E/Project/‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö/New folder'\nINPUT_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'input')\nPATTERN_DIR = os.path.join(BASE_DIR, 'patterns')\nos.makedirs(PATTERN_DIR, exist_ok=True)   # Auto create ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ\n\n# -------------------------------\n# STEP 2: ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô Extract X/Y Transition \n# ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£ ‚Äî ‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏ó‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô\n# -------------------------------\ndef extract_transition_profile_XY(image_path):\n    '''\n    image_path: ‡∏ï‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô 'E/Project/‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö/New folder/input/xxx.png'\n    return: DataFrame ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö X (row) ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ Y (col) patterns\n    '''\n    img = Image.open(image_path).convert('RGB')\n    arr = np.array(img)\n    H, W = arr.shape[:2]\n\n    # X-axis (‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏ô, ‡πÅ‡∏ñ‡∏ß)\n    x_records = []\n    for y in range(H):\n        row = arr[y]\n        diff = np.any(row[1:] != row[:-1], axis=1)\n        x_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [W-1]\n        x_diffs = [x_points[i+1] - x_points[i] for i in range(len(x_points)-1)]\n        x_records.append({\n            'Y': y,\n            'X Points': str(x_points),\n            'X Dif': str(x_diffs),\n            'X Count': len(x_points),\n            'X Dif Count': len(set(x_diffs)),\n            'X Dif Min': min(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0,\n            'X Dif Max': max(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0\n        })\n\n    # Y-axis (‡πÅ‡∏ô‡∏ß‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á, ‡∏Ñ‡∏≠‡∏•‡∏±‡∏°‡∏ô‡πå)\n    y_records = []\n    for x in range(W):\n        col = arr[:, x]\n        diff = np.any(col[1:] != col[:-1], axis=1)\n        y_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [H-1]\n        y_diffs = [y_points[i+1] - y_points[i] for i in range(len(y_points)-1)]\n        y_records.append({\n            'X': x,\n            'Y Points': str(y_points),\n            'Y Dif': str(y_diffs),\n            'Y Count': len(y_points),\n            'Y Dif Count': len(set(y_diffs)),\n            'Y Dif Min': min(y_diffs) if y_diffs else 0,\n            'Y Dif Max': max(y_diffs) if y_diffs else 0\n        })\n\n    return pd.DataFrame(x_records), pd.DataFrame(y_records)\n\n# -------------------------------\n# STEP 3: ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô ‚Äú‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå input‚Äù ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥\n#  ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏∏ image_path ‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á!\n# -------------------------------\nfor fname in sorted(os.listdir(INPUT_DIR)):\n    if fname.lower().endswith(('.png', '.jpg', '.jpeg', '.bmp')):\n        img_path = os.path.join(INPUT_DIR, fname)\n        print(f\"‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏•‡∏±‡∏á‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏°‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ: {img_path}\")\n\n        # Extract transition profiles (X ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ Y)\n        df_x, df_y = extract_transition_profile_XY(img_path)\n\n        # ‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∂‡∏Å‡∏ú‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô CSV ‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠ image_X.csv / image_Y.csv\n        img_base = os.path.splitext(fname)[0]\n        x_csv = os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, f\"{img_base}_X.csv\")\n        y_csv = os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, f\"{img_base}_Y.csv\")\n        df_x.to_csv(x_csv, index=False)\n        df_y.to_csv(y_csv, index=False)\n        print(f\"‡∏ö‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∂‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå output: {x_csv}, {y_csv}\")\n\nprint(\"=== ‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏£‡πá‡∏à‡∏™‡∏¥‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå input ===\")\nprint(\"‚Ä¢ ‡∏ô‡∏≥‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå png/jpg ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ô input/\")\nprint(\"‚Ä¢ ‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà patterns/ ‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥ ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏£‡∏≠‡∏Å image_path ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢\")\n```\n\n---\n\n### **‡∏ß‡∏¥‡∏ò‡∏µ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ (Step by Step ‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏Ñ‡∏ô)**\n1. ‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÑ‡∏ß‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏ô `input/`\n2. ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô ‡πÉ‡∏ô Jupyter/Colab ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ python mybatch.py\n3. ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏™‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏à image_path ‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏¢  \n4. ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏•‡∏±‡∏û‡∏ò‡πå‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå .csv ‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û ‡πÅ‡∏¢‡∏Å X/Y ‚Äî ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ô `patterns/` (‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Ç‡∏≠)\n\n---\n\n### **NOTE ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ ‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤**\n- ‡∏ó‡∏∏‡∏Å path/comment **‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏∏‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å**\n- ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏à‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏Ñ‡∏µ‡∏¢‡πå image_path ‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á ‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏ä‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏° structure\n- Dyslexia-friendly: ‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏î‡∏°‡∏µ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡πà‡∏á‡∏™‡πÄ‡∏ï‡πá‡∏õ, print ‡∏Ç‡∏ì‡∏∞‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô, ‡∏á‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ debug, output ‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà patterns, ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏´‡∏•‡∏á\n---\n\n**‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏™‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏™‡∏ô ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏≤‡∏Å‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà comment ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°, ‡∏ó‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏ö, ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ mapping ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠  \n‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ ‚Äî ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏∏‡∏´‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ï‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πà‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö ultra step-by-step ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏≠‡∏µ‡∏Å‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö!**"
