          "text": "**‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏à‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏ô ‚Äî ‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á‡πÜ ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ß‡∏Å‡∏ß‡∏ô:**\n\n### **‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå input ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß (E:\\Project\\‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö\\New folder\\input)**\n**1.** ‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á ‚Äú‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ (.png, .jpg)‚Äù **‡∏•‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏ô input**  \n**2.** ‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏ô‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô ‚Äú‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏î‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏•‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‚Äù  \n**3.** ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå .csv ‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏•‡∏±‡∏û‡∏ò‡πå‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà `E:\\Project\\‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö\\New folder\\patterns\\` **‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥**\n\n---\n\n## **‡∏™‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏õ 3 ‡∏Ç‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ô ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏´‡∏≤‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°**\n\n1. **‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà input\\\\**\n   - ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á:  \n     `E:\\Project\\‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö\\New folder\\input\\image1.png`\n   - (‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡∏Å‡∏µ‡πà‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏Å‡πá‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ)\n\n2. **‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏î‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ:**\n```python\nimport os\nimport numpy as np\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom PIL import Image\n\nINPUT_DIR = r'E:\\Project\\‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö\\New folder\\input'\nPATTERN_DIR = r'E:\\Project\\‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö\\New folder\\patterns'\nos.makedirs(PATTERN_DIR, exist_ok=True)\n\ndef extract_transition_profile_XY(image_path):\n    img = Image.open(image_path).convert('RGB')\n    arr = np.array(img)\n    H, W = arr.shape[:2]\n    x_records = []\n    for y in range(H):\n        row = arr[y]\n        diff = np.any(row[1:] != row[:-1], axis=1)\n        x_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [W-1]\n        x_diffs = [x_points[i+1] - x_points[i] for i in range(len(x_points)-1)]\n        x_records.append({\n            'Y': y, 'X Points': str(x_points), 'X Dif': str(x_diffs),\n            'X Count': len(x_points), 'X Dif Count': len(set(x_diffs)),\n            'X Dif Min': min(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0, 'X Dif Max': max(x_diffs) if x_diffs else 0\n        })\n    y_records = []\n    for x in range(W):\n        col = arr[:, x]\n        diff = np.any(col[1:] != col[:-1], axis=1)\n        y_points = [0] + (np.where(diff)[0] + 1).tolist() + [H-1]\n        y_diffs = [y_points[i+1] - y_points[i] for i in range(len(y_points)-1)]\n        y_records.append({\n            'X': x, 'Y Points': str(y_points), 'Y Dif': str(y_diffs),\n            'Y Count': len(y_points), 'Y Dif Count': len(set(y_diffs)),\n            'Y Dif Min': min(y_diffs) if y_diffs else 0, 'Y Dif Max': max(y_diffs) if y_diffs else 0\n        })\n    return pd.DataFrame(x_records), pd.DataFrame(y_records)\n\nfor fname in sorted(os.listdir(INPUT_DIR)):\n    if fname.lower().endswith(('.png', '.jpg', '.jpeg', '.bmp')):\n        img_path = os.path.join(INPUT_DIR, fname)\n        df_x, df_y = extract_transition_profile_XY(img_path)\n        base = os.path.splitext(fname)[0]\n        df_x.to_csv(os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, f'{base}_X.csv'), index=False)\n        df_y.to_csv(os.path.join(PATTERN_DIR, f'{base}_Y.csv'), index=False)\n        print(f'‚úî ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏•‡∏±‡∏û‡∏ò‡πå: {base}_X.csv, {base}_Y.csv')\nprint('=== ‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏£‡πá‡∏à‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ö‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏¢ ===')\n```\n\n3. **‡∏î‡∏π‡∏ú‡∏•‡∏•‡∏±‡∏û‡∏ò‡πå .csv ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà patterns\\\\**\n   - ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á:  \n     `E:\\Project\\‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö\\New folder\\patterns\\image1_X.csv`  \n     `E:\\Project\\‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö\\New folder\\patterns\\image1_Y.csv`\n\n---\n\n### **‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏≥‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏° ‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà input ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ**\n- ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå input ‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏°‡∏µ ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°\n- ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏≠ error \"folder ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡πÄ‡∏à‡∏≠\" ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πá‡∏Å path spelling ‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ñ‡∏π‡∏Å ‡∏Å‡∏•‡∏±‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà ‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà error\n\n---\n\n**‡∏™‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏õ: ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå ‚Üí ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏î‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ö‡∏ô = ‡∏à‡∏ö ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏£‡πå‡πÉ‡∏´‡∏°‡πà ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå!**  \n**‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£ ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á error ‡∏´‡∏£‡∏∑‡∏≠ print ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡∏°‡∏≤‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏ï‡∏≠‡∏ö/‡πÅ‡∏Å‡πâ‡∏à‡∏∏‡∏î‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö step-by-step ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏µ‡∏Å‡∏ä‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô**"
